   630→impl Ridge {
   631→    /// Fit a Ridge regression model using coordinate descent
   632→    ///
   633→    /// This implementation uses coordinate descent optimization with L2 regularization
   634→    /// to shrink coefficients toward zero without enforcing sparsity.
   635→    ///
   636→    /// # Arguments
   637→    /// * `x` - Design matrix as ndarray view (n_observations × n_predictors)
